org.apache.poi.ddf

Class EscherComplexProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherProperty
      • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherComplexProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EscherArrayProperty 

    public class EscherComplexProperty
extends EscherProperty
    A complex property differs from a simple property in that the data can not fit inside a 32 bit integer. See the specification for more detailed information regarding exactly what is stored here.(复杂属性与简单属性的不同之处在于，数据无法容纳32位的整元。有关此处存储的内容的更多详细信息，请参阅规范。)
